reviews.text: Overall, a good Dim Sum restaurant where you find good service(something to be greatly appreciated in such restaurants nowadays) and absolutely reasonable prices. Above average food quality. Quality is definitely above the price.
Casual Chinese food for 4 for under 500HKD

Easy to get the table and no waiting was needed since there was spacious.  Unfortunately,  the foods we ordered were tasteless and it was worse than the canteen dishes.  The restaurant manager (male)  was impolite too.
A common traditional Chinese restaurant where people can get dim sum and Cantonese food. Not too bad, not too good. Can't find anything special.
Service is all right and food is delicious !

reviews.text: 流沙奶黃包真流沙😍😋
飲茶食飯好經濟，品質還可以，但假期較難揾位，地下有停車場，幫襯都有3小時免費泊車，再可行商場，好！

Overall, a good Dim Sum restaurant where you find good service(something to be greatly appreciated in such restaurants nowadays) and absolutely reasonable prices. Above average food quality. Quality is definitely above the price.
點心好食！😊👍🍷🌹
食物一般，勝在容易搵位
